      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Which of the following nutritional factors is required for proper collagen assembly in the scar tissue of the patient?</span></span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q8411481",
